                                                               BUSINESS QUESTION
Which customers are highly engaged but not converting into buyers?

                                     QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN login_frequency > 15 
     AND total_purchases < 3 THEN 'High Engagement - Low Buyers'
ELSE 'Others'
END AS customer_group,
COUNT(*) AS customer_count
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY customer_group;

Insight:
There are customers who interact a lot with the platform but are not making purchases. This means interest is there, but something is stopping them from 

Recommendation
We should target these customers with personalized offers, better product display, and maybe simplify the buying process to convert them into actual buyers.
